<br>
“Awww,” Lana gushed and leaned against Clark. “Aren’t they cute?” She brought her hand up to her heart as she said it. ‘Lana Lang, drama queen,’ Chloe thought. ‘But she is being really nice about it.’ Pete opted not to say anything at this point. Chloe was still giving him that look like she wanted to say something, but just couldn’t in front of Clark, so he was trying to tell himself that it was just a game. If he let himself believe otherwise, Lex would be dead in a couple of minutes.<br>
<br>
