<br>
“You’re the one who wanted to come,” Lex reminded him. Pete glared at him.<br>
<br>
“Yeah, yeah. Let’s just get this over with,” Pete said. They walked into the house, where a staunch butler promptly met them.<br>
<br>
“Your father has requested that you join him in the dining room,” the butler said. Lex nodded. “Dinner will be served in ten minutes.” With that, the butler turned on his heel and left the room. Lex grinned at Chloe and then kissed her on her temple.<br>
